Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天也很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海邊很涼快的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮會發黏的  討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹沒來好可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
