Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.84,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（公車站  65路公交海濱公園前下車）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.84,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（水壺裡有茶哦！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.84,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（等你來！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我去拿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠  別勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳正好能探到底  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個  好像溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呼吸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得很嚴重嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就在公車站附近  是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該該該該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發燒嘛…是中暑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事發我簡訊吧  我很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位這麼擔心  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事真的太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我剛聽說的時候真嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼永同學…你也知道我溺水了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鎮子小著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過奈緒做的真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是游泳部的下屆部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮？是怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依媛前輩為春日野君……做人工呼吸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  mouth to mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮…亮平！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  這是悠和小穹的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的祭典  最吸引眼球的鋪子經營的是土耳其三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土耳其三明治？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土耳其三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快來到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fsp-1}嗯  祭典快來的時候  就連現在這段等待開幕的時間都讓人無比期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏祭到來之前  我會把我和奈緒的事情告訴穹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼急的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有各自不同的心靈步幅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要每個人都幸福的話  就要花上許多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我先回去了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪裡不舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  你不是說很快就回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離開我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起上學去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠不可以離開我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠  小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出了什麼事  我肯定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.80,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（沒有新簡訊）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變成這意思  在這裡的左邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這故事原來不是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧那個棒子的木紋形成了中獎的圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大概就是這故事的出處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像個都市傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這裡是破鄉下就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒中…是真的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把假的故事告訴小穹了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:25.06,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（離開這裡吧  悠）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好這有點小禮物要送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹她…不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不是說  小穹她沒事  不要緊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去找小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來找哪兒呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這果然是…悠的自行車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把穹逼到了這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日野君  現在我在車站  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹  小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧  小悠也在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等悠來了我就和他一起離開這個鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續留在這裡悠就會拋棄我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄…小穹？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠過去一直在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…現在的悠變了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從見到你以後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是和媽媽的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕變成孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了爸爸和媽媽  來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是連悠也離開我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明知這麼做無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一想到要被悠拋棄  我就很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人搞不定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  去叫那位鄰家姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛  可愛  大家都可愛極了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  我也想穿浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跳神樂舞  將就一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  費了不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹晚上好  這件浴衣好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹妹妹  有什麼煩惱儘管來找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找中里同學商量只會陷入困境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這是妨礙營業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不妨來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  趕在賣完之前  去吃土耳其三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種場合準備比較花時間  要是奈緒能幫忙就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那個  是穹說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要叫上奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}雖然中獎冰棒是我搞錯了  但我還會分辨哪個彈珠汽水好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}膠環底下的凹槽是圓的話就很甜  是方的話就會有很多氣泡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別解開衣帶
