Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:09.14,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\pos(333,309)\fsp35}现在也在城市
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂初佳  今天的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.46,0:22:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是要送達小姐忘帶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOODBYE HONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.51,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（保健室）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠找到我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間的關係已經眾人皆知了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是抱著初佳小姐來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以說出一直想說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我比你小又不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒工作也掙不了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家很在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  繼續中午的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比你小又不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒工作也掙不了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個手機鈴聲  是留在城市的那傢伙打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的總結
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:57.00,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附录首次！让人在意的下文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:23:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:23:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續


